<br>
<br>
With this I have:<br>
(unbuffed)<br>
<br>
Ac:826<br>
Hp: 1730<br>
<br>
Str: 122<br>
Sta: 151<br>
Dex: 94<br>
Agi: 117<br>
Int: 102<br>
Wis: 201<br>
