<br>
And some nice basic resist, and the chance to change some items when I need resist gear without loosing too much wis.<br>
<br>
It’s not totaly uber, but gets you decent stat without the use of Velious Quest Armor. As you might have guessed I am trying to get AC and HP items, but that’s the beauty of the druid class, you can choose to play it in so many ways, and its really up to you, to find out what suits you best.<br>
<br>
