 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uarkinia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>arkinia</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/31/01 12:19:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3358.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Non-WIS Equip</span><hr size=1> Boots: Definitly Barbed Dragon scale or Iksar hide for non Wisdom(Vellium quest ones have AGI...not bad.  I use Grey Suede boots myself.<br>
<br>
Legs: Your not going to be able to avoid a lot of wisdom.  You just cannot stay at 200.  I have about 230+ now, and use Nature Walker Legs.  These or any vellius/PoH druid armor (even ES), is good since the +mana helps.  <br>
<br>
Arms: Vermic arms arnt bad, but I currently use Crystal Chittnin Armplates. 18 ac 5 str/sta 10 hp.  Nice non wis stats.<br>
<br>
Gloves: Crystal Chitnin Gloves have like 24 ac 40 mana or something, very nice.  I use PoG quest gloves for the str and 55 mana + saves, but Crystal ones are nice.<br>
<br>
Helm: Frog crown is nice, ive worn one forever now...Looking to upgrade to dain crown soon.<br>
<br>
Ring: Dyjarns amethist and Runed Etched Wedding band are nice non wis stats.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urandomuser.showPublicProfile?language=EN>random user</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/31/01 4:55:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3358.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Non-WIS Equip</span><hr size=1> Crystal Chitin Circlet was not changed, it is still ac12 wis3 and some other stats<br>
<br>
For helm there is also circlet of tallon (AC:18/CR:9/MR:9/PR:9) or circlet of vallon (AC:18/FR:9/MR:9/DR:9).  Also the frozen turban (AC:25/Agi:15/Effect:EndureCold) but you might not be able to convince people to give it to you...<br>
<br>
For rings, if you can get it, the 9th coldain ring (AC:9/Str:9/Sta:9/HP:50/MR:9/Effect:ShieldOfTheEighth) is very nice (and all doable with one strong group, or one group + a couple others).<br>
<br>
Also you may want to look at the Knotted Turtlebone Ring, which has ok stats but also has EB (AC:5/Str:3/Mana:35/HP:25/Effect:EnduringBreath).<br>
